---
title: Quick Indian-Style Creamy Beef with Mash & Steamed Veggies
description: Tender beef is offset perfectly with a creamy tomato-based sauce in tonight’s dinner. Add a classic combination of mashed
potatoes and steamed veggies to the plate to tie this dish up with a scrumptious bow.

